msgid "[.no-hyphens]#*assign-seek*#"
msgstr "*寻找任务*"

#. type: Table
#: _versions/main/guides/_includes/smallrye-kafka-incoming.adoc
#, fuzzy
msgid ""
"Assign partitions and optionally seek to offsets, instead of subscribing to topics. A comma-separating list of triplets in form of `<topic>:|<partition>|:<offset>` to assign statically to the consumer and seek to the given offsets. Offset `0` seeks to beginning and offset `-1` seeks to the end of the topic-partition. If the topic is omitted the configured topic will be used. If the offset is omitted partitions are assigned to the consumer but won't be seeked to offset.\n"
"\n"
"Type: _string_"
msgstr "指定分区并可选择搜索偏移量，而不是订阅主题。以逗号分隔的 `<topic>:|<partition>|:<offset>` 形式的三元组列表，用于静态分配给消费者并寻址到给定的偏移量。偏移量 `0` 搜索主题分区的起点，偏移量 `-1` 搜索主题分区的终点。如果省略了主题，将使用配置的主题。如果省略偏移量，分区将被分配给用户，但不会搜索到偏移量。"

